    "comment": "Rationale: The figure shows the synaptic co-localization of 4E-BP1 with synapse in hippocampal neurons (P2; 14 DIV), furthermore 4E-EBP1 colocalize with PSD-95, postsynaptic marker.\n\n24/9/2017 Pim\n- Literal: \"The mTOR-positive regions were observed in the dendritic shaft in a diffuse pattern that extended into synaptic regions (Fig. (Fig.33Al). Consistent with the notion of postsynaptic localization of these proteins, double labeling with PSD-95 showed the signals from eIF-4E, 4E-BP1, and mTOR at synaptic regions almost completely overlapped with PSD-95 signals.\". Experimental description: Sprague-Dawley",
